---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
// High-Performance B2B SEO Page targeting Industrial Conveyor Belts in Sri Lanka
---

<Layout 
	title="Conveyor Belt Suppliers & Replacement Sri Lanka | E Lanka World"
	description="Leading conveyor belt manufacturers & suppliers in Sri Lanka. Premium PVC, heavy-duty rubber, fabric, and canvas conveyor belt replacement at unbeatable prices."
>
	
	<main>
		<nav class="belts-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
			<div class="belts-container">
				<div class="belts-crumbs">
					<a href="/">Home</a>
					<span class="divider">&gt;</span>
					<a href="/shop">Shop</a>
					<span class="divider">&gt;</span>
					<a href="/conveyor">Conveyor Systems</a>
					<span class="divider">&gt;</span>
					<span class="belts-current">Conveyor Belts</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<section class="belts-hero">
			<div class="belts-container">
				<div class="belts-hero-content">
					<span class="belts-badge">Industrial Grade Solutions</span>
					<h1>Conveyor Belt Suppliers & Splicing Replacement in Sri Lanka</h1>
					<p>Minimize critical factory downtime with high-durability conveyor belting. From heavy-duty multi-ply rubber to hygienic food-grade PVC profiles, we source and fit the exact structural specifications your industrial lines demand.</p>
					
					<div class="belts-hero-ctas">
						<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="belts-btn-primary">Inquire Belt Price Now</a>
						<a href="#replacement-guide" class="belts-btn-secondary">Replacement Procedure</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="belts-trust-bar">
			<div class="belts-container">
				<div class="trust-grid">
					<div class="trust-stat">
						<span class="stat-num">100%</span>
						<p>Custom Engineered Cut-to-Length</p>
					</div>
					<div class="trust-stat">
						<span class="stat-num">Ready</span>
						<p>Local Sri Lankan Stockpile</p>
					</div>
					<div class="trust-stat">
						<span class="stat-num">Inline</span>
						<p>Speed & Dynamic Tension Synced</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="trust-statement-box">
					<div class="badge-icon">🛡️</div>
					<p><strong>E Lanka World International</strong> is a premier structural choice for processing automation. We have proudly supplied, configured, and maintained thousands of diverse conveyor belts, tracking profiles, and system accessories for leading tea packaging factories, bottling plants, food processors, and heavy industrial facilities across Sri Lanka.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="belts-catalog-section">
			<div class="belts-container">
				<h2 class="belts-section-title">Premium Conveyor Belt Materials & Variants</h2>
				<p class="belts-section-subtitle">We supply open-ended and endless tracking configurations precisely sized for local industrial machinery operations.</p>
				
				<div class="belts-catalog-grid">
					
					<article class="belts-product-card">
						<div class="belts-image-frame">
							<img 
								src="/products/heavy-duty-rubber-fabric-conveyor-belts.webp" 
								alt="Heavy-duty industrial rubber conveyor belt material and canvas multi-ply tracking variants" 
								width="600" 
								height="337" 
								loading="eager"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="belts-card-body">
							<h3>Heavy-Duty Rubber & Fabric Belts</h3>
							<p>Engineered for aggressive abrasion setups. High-tensile canvas conveyor belt options, cotton canvas reinforcement layers, and premium raw rubber conveyor belt material built to handle rough aggregate runs or bulky boxed shipping runs.</p>
							<div class="card-footer">
								<span class="price-tag">Best Market Price</span>
								<a href="rubber" class="card-link">Learn More &rarr;</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="belts-product-card">
						<div class="belts-image-frame">
							<img 
								src="/products/pvc-pu-food-grade-conveyor-belting.webp" 
								alt="Food grade PVC conveyor belt and chemical resistant PU processing bands" 
								width="600" 
								height="337" 
								loading="lazy"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="belts-card-body">
							<h3>PVC & Food-Grade PU Belting</h3>
							<p>The perfect sanitary matching choice for food processing and electronic production lines. Our premium green and white PVC conveyor belt configurations resist oils, processing grease, and moisture common in local Sri Lankan packaging setups.</p>
							<div class="card-footer">
								<span class="price-tag">FDA Certified Materials</span>
								<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="card-link">Request Quote &rarr;</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="belts-product-card">
						<div class="belts-image-frame">
							<img 
								src="/products/modular-cleated-curved-conveyor-belts.webp" 
								alt="Modular plastic chain, cleated profiles, and curved conveyor loop sections" 
								width="600" 
								height="337" 
								loading="lazy"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="belts-card-body">
							<h3>Flat, Modular, Cleated & Curved</h3>
							<p>Custom structural configurations to match your automation blueprint footprint. Includes interlocking modular plastic mesh, horizontal curved flight belts, and integrated cleated profiles to safely lift products vertically without slippage.</p>
							<div class="card-footer">
								<span class="price-tag">Custom Manufactured</span>
								<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="card-link">Request Quote &rarr;</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="belts-product-card">
						<div class="belts-image-frame">
							<img 
								src="/products/conveyor-belt-replacement-splicing-service.webp" 
								alt="Professional conveyor belt replacement procedure and endless joint splicing in Sri Lanka" 
								width="600" 
								height="337" 
								loading="lazy"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="belts-card-body">
							<h3>Endless Splicing & Replacement</h3>
							<p>We execute standard mechanical lacing configurations along with premium seamless hot vulcanizing joint processing and cold chemical bonds to create flawless, high-durability endless conveyor belts on your machine frames.</p>
							<div class="card-footer">
								<span class="price-tag">On-Site Execution</span>
								<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="card-link">Book Engineers &rarr;</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</article>

				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="replacement-guide" class="belts-seo-article">
			<div class="belts-container">
				<div class="article-wrapper">
					<h2>Conveyor Belt Replacement Procedure & Support Near Me</h2>
					<p>
						When an active line suffers tracking damage, understanding the precise <strong>conveyor belt replacement procedure</strong> keeps your plant operators safe and protects structural gearboxes from early mechanical stress. Over-tensioning can bend drive shafts, while under-tensioning leads to track slippage, material loss, and high heat wear.
					</p>
					
					<div class="procedure-steps">
						<div class="step-item">
							<h4>1. Isolation & Tension Release</h4>
							<p>Completely cut system electrical inputs. Back off the mechanical take-up alignment screws to smoothly remove tension from the worn tracking belt strip safely.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step-item">
							<h4>2. Tracking Inspection & Cleaning</h4>
							<p>Before pulling a fresh profile, inspect the underlying stainless slider bed or internal roller idlers for built-up residue or alignment damage.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step-item">
							<h4>3. Splicing Execution</h4>
							<p>Depending on structural space limitations, open-ended tracking bands can be threaded directly through the chassis framework and joined seamlessly into an endless setup via hot vulcanizing presses or high-grade mechanical hooks.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p>
						Stop searching for unreliable <em>"conveyor belt replacement near me"</em> across untracked networks. Our local mobile engineering division arrives directly to your facility floor anywhere in Sri Lanka with complete alignment toolkits to ensure your tracking tracking parameters scale perfectly.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="belts-navigation-hub">
			<div class="belts-container">
				<h3>Explore Material Handling & Packaging Directories</h3>
				<div class="nav-links-grid">
					<a href="/" class="hub-link main-link">Home Page</a>
					<a href="/conveyor" class="hub-link main-link">Main Conveyor Systems Hub</a>
					<a href="/shop" class="hub-link main-link">Other Packaging Machinery Shop</a>
					
					<a href="#" class="hub-link placeholder-link">Conveyor Rollers & Idlers (Coming Soon)</a>
					<a href="#" class="hub-link placeholder-link">Conveyor Motors & Drives (Coming Soon)</a>
					<a href="#" class="hub-link placeholder-link">Vulcanizing & Splicing Services (Coming Soon)</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* --- CSS ROOT ARCHITECTURE & UTILITIES --- */
	.belts-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.5rem;
	}
	
	/* --- BREADCRUMB --- */
	.belts-breadcrumb {
		background-color: #f1f5f9;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
		padding: 0.8rem 0;
	}
	.belts-crumbs {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: #64748b;
	}
	.belts-crumbs a {
		color: #2563eb;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s ease;
	}
	.belts-crumbs a:hover {
		color: #1d4ed8;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.belts-crumbs .divider {
		color: #cbd5e1;
	}
	.belts-current {
		color: #0f172a;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	/* --- HERO SECTION --- */
	.belts-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001f3f 0%, #022c54 100%);
		color: #ffffff;
		padding: 5.5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.belts-hero-content {
		max-width: 850px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.belts-badge {
		background-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
		color: #60a5fa;
		padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
	}
	.belts-hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 1.2rem 0;
	}
	.belts-hero p {
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #cbd5e1;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}
	.belts-hero-ctas {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.2rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.belts-btn-primary {
		background-color: #25D366;
		color: #ffffff;
		font-weight: 700;
		padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3);
	}
	.belts-btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		background-color: #1eb954;
	}
	.belts-btn-secondary {
		background-color: transparent;
		color: #ffffff;
		font-weight: 700;
		padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		border: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
		transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
	}
	.belts-btn-secondary:hover {
		background-color: #ffffff;
		color: #001f3f;
	}

	/* --- TRUST CREDENTIAL BAR --- */
	.belts-trust-bar {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		background-color: #ffffff;
	}
	.trust-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	.trust-stat {
		background-color: #f8fafc;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
	}
	.stat-num {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #2563eb;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}
	.trust-stat p {
		color: #475569;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.trust-statement-box {
		background-color: #eff6ff;
		border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: left;
	}
	.badge-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
	}
	.trust-statement-box p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #1e3a8a;
	}

	/* --- CATALOG GRID SECTION --- */
	.belts-catalog-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background-color: #f8fafc;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.belts-section-title {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		color: #001f3f;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.belts-section-subtitle {
		color: #64748b;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}
	.belts-catalog-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 2.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}
	.belts-product-card {
		background-color: #ffffff;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
		border-top: 5px solid #2563eb;
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease;
	}
	.belts-product-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
	}
	.belts-image-frame {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 600 / 337; /* Forces absolute rendering ratio locking aspect framework */
		overflow: hidden;
		background-color: #cbd5e1;
	}
	.belts-image-frame img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		display: block;
	}
	.belts-card-body {
		padding: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}
	.belts-card-body h3 {
		color: #001f3f;
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.belts-card-body p {
		color: #475569;
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}
	.card-footer {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
		padding-top: 1rem;
	}
	.price-tag {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #16a34a;
		background-color: #f0fdf4;
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	.card-link {
		color: #2563eb;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
	.card-link:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	/* --- SEO ARTICLE TEXT MODULE --- */
	.belts-seo-article {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background-color: #ffffff;
		color: #334155;
	}
	.article-wrapper {
		max-width: 950px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.belts-seo-article h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: #001f3f;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
	}
	.belts-seo-article p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	.belts-seo-article strong {
		color: #0f172a;
	}
	.procedure-steps {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2.5rem 0;
	}
	.step-item {
		background-color: #f8fafc;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 3px solid #64748b;
	}
	.step-item h4 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		color: #001f3f;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}
	.step-item p {
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin: 0;
		color: #475569;
	}

	/* --- BOTTOM INTERNAL NAVIGATION HUB --- */
	.belts-navigation-hub {
		padding: 4.5rem 0;
		background-color: #0f172a;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.belts-navigation-hub h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #f8fafc;
	}
	.nav-links-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.hub-link {
		padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}
	.main-link {
		background-color: #1e293b;
		color: #f1f5f9;
		border: 1px solid #334155;
	}
	.main-link:hover {
		background-color: #2563eb;
		color: #ffffff;
		border-color: #2563eb;
	}
	.placeholder-link {
		background-color: transparent;
		color: #64748b;
		border: 1px dashed #334155;
		pointer-events: none; /* Keeps placeholder safe until linked later */
	}

	/* --- SYSTEM RESPONSIVE MEDIA QUERIES --- */
	@media (max-width: 992px) {
		.trust-grid, .procedure-steps {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1rem;
		}
		.trust-statement-box {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.belts-catalog-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
		.belts-hero {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
		.belts-section-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}
		.belts-hero h1 {
			font-size: 1.85rem;
		}
	}
</style>